sources.title: Ernst Lubitsch's "KOHLHIESEL TOECHTER" (aka "Kohlhiesel's Daughters"-1920)
sources.description: German title cards with French subtitles only, sorry! starring Emil Jannings from "Blue Angel" and Gustav von Wangenheim from "Nosferatu, eine Symphonie des Grauens". A very funny romantic comedy with the most delightful ending. more info on http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0011371/
